## 작업별 권장 참조 순서

- **백엔드 API/모듈/DB**  
  `agent/backend/spec/backend_architecture_spec.md` → `agent/common/spec_driven_development_guidelines.md` → `agent/common/schema.md` → `agent/common/openapi_spec_backend.yaml` → `agent/common/proposal.md`

- **OAuth/인증 (백엔드 주도)**  
  `agent/backend/guidelines/oauth_implementation_guidelines.md` → `agent/backend/spec/backend_architecture_spec_producer.md` (1.3) → `agent/common/openapi_spec_backend.yaml` → `agent/common/openapi_spec_frontend.yaml` (`/api/auth/refresh-bridge`) → `agent/frontend/spec/frontend_architecture_spec.md` (3.1)

- **프론트엔드 페이지/라우팅**  
  `agent/frontend/spec/frontend_architecture_spec.md` (특히 §2 페이지 구조 및 라우팅 맵) → `agent/common/screen_flowchart.mermaid` (화면 전환·탭 흐름 확인) → `agent/common/spec_driven_development_guidelines.md` → `agent/frontend/guidelines/frontend_development_guidelines.md` → `agent/common/openapi_spec_backend.yaml` → `agent/common/openapi_spec_frontend.yaml` → `agent/common/proposal.md`

- **프론트엔드 컴포넌트 구조/컨벤션**  
  `agent/frontend/spec/frontend_components_structure_spec.md` → `agent/frontend/guidelines/frontend_component_conventions_guidelines.md` → `agent/frontend/spec/frontend_architecture_spec.md` (라우팅 그룹/탭 매핑 확인) → `agent/frontend/guidelines/frontend_development_guidelines.md` (Storybook·코드 스플리팅·성능·**§9 접근성/`buildAriaLabel`**·**§10 리다이렉트 원칙**; OAuth 계약은 명세·`oauth_implementation_guidelines.md` 참조)

- **데이터·엔티티·스키마**  
  `agent/common/schema.md` → `agent/backend/spec/backend_architecture_spec.md` → `agent/common/openapi_spec_backend.yaml`

- **프론트엔드 Route Handler (BFF·인프라)**  
  `agent/frontend/spec/frontend_architecture_spec.md` (§5.1 Route Handler 표) → `agent/common/openapi_spec_frontend.yaml` → `agent/frontend/guidelines/frontend_development_guidelines.md` (ISR·`/api/revalidate` 등)

- **전체 시스템 구조·배포**  
  `agent/common/architecture.mermaid` → `agent/common/proposal.md` → `agent/backend/spec/backend_architecture_spec.md` / `agent/frontend/spec/frontend_architecture_spec.md` (지침은 `agent/backend/guidelines/`·`agent/frontend/guidelines/` 내 해당 문서 참고)

- **기획·스택·배포 정책**  
  `agent/common/proposal.md` → `agent/common/architecture.mermaid`

- **관측성·모니터링**  
  `validation.md` (통합 검증) → `frontend_event_instrumentation.md` (프론트 계측) → `product_kpi_contract.md`·`event_dictionary.md`·`aggregation_pipeline.md` (KPI 정의·이벤트·집계) → `product_kpi_runbook.md` (알림·장애 대응)

- **UI/UX·디자인 원칙·Figma**  
  - **화면 구현(Figma→코드)**: `agent/design/guidelines/design_to_code_guidelines.md` → `agent/design/spec/design_tokens.json` → `agent/design/spec/design_principle.json`(터치 타겟 44px, WCAG 2.1 AA, 반응형 브레이크포인트, LCP/FID/CLS·번들 예산, 레이아웃·챗봇 톤 등) → `agent/frontend/guidelines/frontend_development_guidelines.md`  
  - **코드·웹을 Figma에 반영·MCP 쓰기/캡처**: `agent/design/guidelines/code_to_design_guidelines.md`  
  - **DS 워크플로우(수집→변환→연동)**: `agent/design/guidelines/design_system_collection_guidelines.md` + `agent/design/temp/figma-ds-component-progress.md` → `agent/design/spec/figma-variables-and-styles.md` → `agent/design/guidelines/design_tokens_conversion_guidelines.md` → `agent/design/spec/design_tokens.json` → `agent/design/guidelines/design_system_integration_guidelines.md` → `client/src/app/globals.css`
  - **DS 분석·권장 수정사항 정리**: `agent/design/guidelines/design_system_analysis_guidelines.md`(체크리스트·운영) → `agent/design/temp/` 피드백 문서 갱신
